main event: A UFO sighting was reported on April 11, 1956, in Passaic, New Jersey, observed for approximately 1 minute and 3 seconds.
interesting points: The UFO had sharply outlined edges but disappeared below the horizon., The exact direction of the flight path was not provided., There were attempts by the author to seek information from the Air Force about the UFO., A questioner related to the UFO sighting had missing questions that could not be written on., The report contained a technical information sheet referencing a very bright white object in the sky.
witness description: The witness was a male student with 8 years of grade school education.
